[3] UN Mission for Ebola Emergency Response (UNMEER) External Situation Report 7 Apr 2015
Date: Thu 2 Apr 2015
Source: UNMEER [edited]
http://ebolaresponse.un.org/sites/default/files/150401_-_unmeer_external_situation_report.pdf


Key points
----------
- As a contribution to ongoing efforts by the affected countries to design their national EVD recovery strategies, UNDP [United Nations Development Program] has published a report on "Recovering from the Ebola Crisis."
- NERC [National Ebola Response Centre] Sierra Leone confirm that the child in Kailahun reported to have died of Ebola on 3 Apr 2015 had actually died of other causes.
- Sensitization campaigns gather pace in Forecariah and Coyah, Guinea.

